  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to identify if intensive language training, consisting mainly of
      computer-based object naming, together with electrical brain stimulation, will lead to an
      improvement of language functions in patients that suffer from language disturbances after a
      stroke.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
